# Admin Studio — build-time config (optional).
#
# By default the Studio talks to the admin API at the SAME ORIGIN under /admin
# (it is served behind the same Caddy edge). You normally do NOT need to set
# anything here — the operator can also override the base URL on the Login
# screen at runtime.
#
# Set this only if you want to bake in a different default base URL at build
# time (e.g. when the Studio is hosted separately from the API):
# VITE_ADMIN_API_BASE=/admin

# NEVER put the admin key here. It is pasted at runtime on the Login screen and
# kept in sessionStorage only.
